## Estrutura de Pastas

```
app/
├── components/
│   ├── atoms/       # UButton wraps, ícones customizados, badges
│   ├── molecules/   # StatCard, SearchInput, UserMenu
│   ├── organisms/   # AppSidebar, AppHeader, DataTable, FormPanel
│   └── templates/   # DashboardLayout, AuthLayout
├── composables/     # useAuth, useTable, useDashboard
├── pages/           # index.vue, users/index.vue, settings.vue
├── layouts/         # default.vue, auth.vue
└── types/           # index.ts (interfaces e enums)
```

