## Componentes Nuxt UI — Mapa de Uso

| Categoria  | Componentes                                                                 |
|------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Layout     | `UDashboardLayout`, `UDashboardPanel`, `USidebar`, `UMain`, `UContainer`   |
| Navegação  | `UNavigationLinks`, `UNavigationMenu`, `UBreadcrumb`                        |
| Dados      | `UTable`, `UPagination`                                                     |
| Formulários| `UForm`, `UFormField`, `UInput`, `USelect`, `UCheckbox`, `UTextarea`, `USwitch` |
| Feedback   | `UAlert`, `UToast`, `UProgress`, `USkeleton`                                |
| Overlay    | `UModal`, `UDrawer`, `UPopover`, `UDropdownMenu`, `UTooltip`                |
| Elementos  | `UButton`, `UBadge`, `UAvatar`, `UCard`, `UIcon`, `UChip`, `USeparator`    |
| Misc       | `UCommandPalette`, `UColorModeButton`, `UColorModeToggle`                   |

