## Anti-Padrões — NUNCA faça

```vue
<!-- ❌ cor hardcoded -->
<p class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">...</p>
<!-- ✅ token CSS -->
<p class="text-(--ui-primary)">...</p>

<!-- ❌ sintaxe Tailwind v3 com colchetes -->
<p class="text-[--ui-text-highlighted] bg-[--ui-bg-muted]">...</p>
<!-- ✅ sintaxe Tailwind v4 com parênteses -->
<p class="text-(--ui-text-highlighted) bg-(--ui-bg-muted)">...</p>

<!-- ❌ HTML nativo no lugar de componente Nuxt UI -->
<button class="bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded">Salvar</button>
<!-- ✅ componente Nuxt UI -->
<UButton color="primary">Salvar</UButton>

<!-- ❌ ícone não-Lucide -->
<i class="fas fa-home"></i>
<!-- ✅ Lucide via UIcon -->
<UIcon name="i-lucide-home" />

<!-- ❌ import manual desnecessário -->
<script setup lang="ts">
import { ref } from 'vue'
import MyComponent from '~/components/MyComponent.vue'
</script>
<!-- ✅ auto-import do Nuxt -->
<script setup lang="ts">
const count = ref(0)
</script>

<!-- ❌ link interno com <a> -->
<a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
<!-- ✅ NuxtLink -->
<NuxtLink to="/dashboard">Dashboard</NuxtLink>
```

